      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive preservation. This vehicle remains in showroom-fresh condition, boasting a flawless exterior with a deep, mirror-like finish and absolutely no rock chips, swirls, or imperfections. The interior is equally pristine, featuring supple, uncreased leather that still carries its original factory aroma, with every electronic component, button, and dial functioning with crisp precision. Mechanically, this car is peerless; it has been meticulously maintained by a single owner with a comprehensive, chronological service history performed exclusively by authorized master technicians. It has been strictly garage-kept in a climate-controlled environment and has never been driven in inclement weather. From the spotless, dust-free engine bay to the untouched undercarriage, this is a collector-grade vehicle that satisfies the most discerning standards. Sale includes all original keys, factory manuals, and the original window sticker.",
